well

7
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,690
for the Chinese Communist Party.

8
00:00:24,690 --> 00:00:28,680
I mean, personally I’m more concerned about
all the people,

9
00:00:28,680 --> 00:00:29,940
mainly in China,

10
00:00:29,940 --> 00:00:33,070
who have gotten sick because the Chinese Communist
Party

11
00:00:33,070 --> 00:00:37,149
