instead of stopping it when they had the chance.

13
00:00:39,679 --> 00:00:43,489
But you’ve got to feel for the Chinese regime
just a little bit.

14
00:00:43,489 --> 00:00:48,170
I mean, Chinese leader Xi Jinping even disappeared
for a little while.

15
00:00:48,170 --> 00:00:50,480
That led to rumors that he was sick.

16
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:54,380
Especially after people began sharing a video
of him dry coughing.

17
